==English==
===Etymology===
Coined by the late American [[comedian]] [[w:Billy_Debeck|Billy Debeck]] (1923)

===Pronunciation===
[[w:X_Sampa|X-Sampa]] /hi:bi:dZ)i:bi:z/

===Noun===
'''heebie-jeebies'''
# (''uncountable'') A general feeling of [[uneasiness]], [[fear]], or [[nausea]].
#:''I don't mind worms, but spiders give me the '''heebie-jeebies'''.''

===Synonyms===
*[[give somebody the creeps]]
*[[give somebody the willies]]

